sentences.content: Speech modeling allows me to get clear, correct examples (models) of sounds, words and sentences to pronounce properly.
And by reciting then obscuring the model prompt, this modeling technique will also help me exercise my "short" term memory because it requires me to remember the prompt before recognition begins.
Ultimately, this technique can help me with receptive, retention and expressive skills.
